4. Larentinam. Laurentia or Larentina, the wife of Famula, according to the myth, and nurse of Romulus; Liv. i. 4 ; Macrob. i. 10 3 Aul. Gell. vi. 7 ; Lact. i. 20. She is mentioned again contemptuously, ch. 25 (bis).
